            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="imagessouth/desserts/Payasam.jpg" alt="payasam">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Payasam</h3>
                <p>Soft paneer (cottage cheese) dumplings soaked in sweetened, thickened milk, flavored with cardamom and saffron.</p>
                <p>Price: &#8377;200</p>
                <div class="quantity">
                    <button class="minus-btn">-</button>
                    <input type="text" class="qty-input" value="0" readonly>
                    <button class="plus-btn">+</button>
                </div>
                <button class="heart-btn"><i class="fas fa-heart"></i></button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="imagessouth/desserts/Pongal.jpg" alt="pongal">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Pongal</h3>
                <p>A sweet pudding-like dessert made with semolina, flour, or carrots, cooked in ghee (clarified butter) with sugar and flavored with cardamom and nuts.</p>
                <p>Price: &#8377;150</p>
                <div class="quantity">
                    <button class="minus-btn">-</button>
                    <input type="text" class="qty-input" value="0" readonly>
                    <button class="plus-btn">+</button>
                </div>
                <button class="heart-btn"><i class="fas fa-heart"></i></button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="imagessouth/desserts/Rava Laddoo.jpg" alt="laddoo">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Rava Laddoo</h3>
                <p>It is typically churned and frozen to create a smooth and creamy texture.</p>
                <p>Price: &#8377;150</p>
